@FitnessFanatic: "Yeah, so I used to struggle with disordered eating and low self-esteem. But when I started focusing on my fitness and nutrition, I realized that I had the power to take control of my own body. I started sharing my journey with others, and it really helped me connect with like-minded individuals who were going through similar struggles."

